<body><p><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>当发送者收到了一个窗口为</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>0</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>的应答，发送者便停止发送，等待接收者的下一个应答。但是如果这个窗口不为</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>0</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>的应答在传输过程丢失，发送者一直等待下去，而接收者以为发送者已经收到该应答，等待接收新数据，这样双方就相互等待，从而产生死锁。</span></p></body>
</html>
</richcontent>
